            <title>[SOLR-17152] UI: Cloud Graph misaligned</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-17152</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The cloud graph is badly mis-aligned. If you have many nodes/replicas, it is cut off on the right margin and also overlaps the legend box.&lt;/p&gt;

